title: Video Collection of Ayrton Senna's death
description:
12 videos, at low quality, showing the fact of the death and trying to understand what happened that day with Senna&#039;s death and Ratzenberger&#039;s the day before.

I uploaded this folder because there is nothing similar for download as I saw after searching for some good quality videos.

At least, now, we have a collection and maybe someone can find some better videos and give me a ring!

Good downloading! I&#039;ll be seeding for the first week!
